additionalProperty.name: Warning
additionalProperty.value: Not to be used for any purpose, or in any manner, contrary to this label unless authorised. Surfaces, particularly floors will become slippery once sprayed. Remove excess with paper towel. BEWARE: Intentional misuse by deliberately concentrating and inhaling contents can be harmful or fatal. May irritate the eyes and skin. Avoid contact with eyes and skin. Do not inhale spray mist. Keep out of reach of children. Read safety precaution. Keep out of reach of children. Do not spray into the air, only spray on surface or into hard to reach places.
